description:
“Looking for that blessed hope, and the glorious appearing of the great God and our Saviour Jesus Christ...""
Titus 2:13
.
Behold, I tell you a mystery: We shall not all sleep, but we shall all be changed--in a moment, in the twinkling of an eye, at the last trumpet. For the trumpet will sound, and the dead will be raised incorruptible, and we shall be changed.
1 Corinthians 15:52-52
.
Are you prepared for the catching away of the saints? In the twinkling of an eye. You won't be able to get ready, you must be ready.
.
Time is so short.
.
Like the old chorus goes...
.
There's no time to change your mind. The Father spoke, the demons dined, the Son has come, and you've been left behind.
.
Don't be left behind. Repent and believe the gospel. Forgive everyone and be forgiven. Love covers a multitude of sin.
.
Jesus bless you all! 🙏🔥❤
.
